snippet.title: Lift Attendant - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
If you had the power to control elevators do you think you could do better than the system? Well now you can!

Introducing Lift Attendant, a minimalist puzzle game where you control elevators to transport passengers to their desired floors!

Wishlist on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3035940/Lift_Attendant
